    "description": "Restful Booker API collection organized by test case ID.\n\nMaps 1:1 to Playwright tests in:\n- tests/api/auth.spec.ts (AU01-AU02)\n- tests/api/booking.spec.ts (BK01-BK13)\n- tests/api/booking.lifecycle.spec.ts (LC01-LC02)\n\nKnown Bugs:\n- BUG-001: POST /booking returns 200 instead of 201\n- BUG-002: Accepts bookings with empty required fields\n- BUG-003: Accepts bookings with negative totalprice\n- BUG-004: Accepts checkout before checkin\n- BUG-005: PUT accepts invalid data\n- BUG-006: PATCH accepts invalid data\n- BUG-007: POST /auth returns 200 instead of 401 for invalid credentials\n- BUG-008: DELETE returns 201 instead of 204; GET /ping returns 201 instead of 200",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
